{"tid":1641511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫男藝人化身Joker小丑上阿姐節目","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T16:03:08.000Z","uid":92376,"like":16,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"edc3c666f9151ecf522e20b7b085d47e101aea12","tid":1641511,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zNckBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zNckBj.jpg&h=ef439977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjYi0Bk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjYi0Bk.jpg&h=c617bc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jv9if9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJv9if9G.jpg&h=030b5789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前宣布太太懷上第3胎的藝人黃祥興(又名黃長興、黃致豪)出席節目錄影，談到再當爸爸時，他坦言：「預產期係明年1月尾，我哋都想講生豬B。（開刀？）係，因為上兩胎都係。」談到BB性別，祥興(長興/致豪)表示：「我哋都冇乜所謂，因為已經有個『好』字，呢次係最後一個喇，本來都冇諗住，但佢嚟到我哋梗係歡迎。（為免再有，你絕育？）可以考慮，如果唔麻煩嘅話，而且聽講男性絕育，有需要嘅話可以解番開。」祥興(長興/致豪)坦言日後要照顧三個小朋友確實吃力，所以已情商黃媽媽幫手：「本來我媽咪退咗休，生活休閒，依家要佢幫手照顧兩個大嘅，好彩佢肯。」 <br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你睇下佢幾戇鳩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ab38c9a7c81b11973f132ea2a08297713580f3","tid":1641511,"uid":76098,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"似cosplay勾二嫂比人打柒多d"},{"pid":"d4c9bde41dabe8ee6cacab4c23fb3cf3d4efd56b","tid":1641511,"uid":317979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:09:19.000Z","msg":"拉得"},{"pid":"5a1b4f966b3bbd22d70f6b3edf48a8246d7aa596","tid":1641511,"uid":25754,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"拎把槍出黎爆牙姐頭-.-"},{"pid":"f290e2ddc32e299e96dab104069e1d2ec870edec","tid":1641511,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":